  "description": "Celebrate your graduate in style on Lake Travis! Perfect graduation party cruises for high school or college grads with 14-75 guests, professional service, and unforgettable memories. Your graduate worked hard for this achievement - celebrate with a Lake Travis cruise they'll never forget! Whether high school or college graduation, a boat party brings friends and family together for the perfect send-off before the next chapter. Professional captain and crew, premium sound for graduate's playlist, swimming and floating for summer celebrations, BYOB for adult guests, space for speeches and toasts, photo opportunities with graduate, customizable party decorations in school colors, accommodate friends AND family together, relaxed celebration atmosphere, creates lasting memories with classmates. Fleet accommodates all sizes: Day Tripper (14 guests intimate, $195/hr), Me Seeks the Irony (25 guests, $295/hr), Clever Girl (50-75 guests big celebration, $495/hr). Popular timing: May-June graduation season, 2-4 hour formats. Packages: Standard cruise, Essentials (+$100-200/hr with party coordination), Ultimate (+$250-350/hr with complete party setup). Book early - graduation season fills 8-12 weeks in advance."
